2003-10-27  Giulio Eulisse  <giulio.eulisse@cern.ch>

	* IgSoMaterialMap.cc (setDefaultMaterials): cosmetic fixes.

	* IgSoMaterialMap.cc (IgSoMaterialMap): now reads one single file,
	as pointed by environment variable SO_MATERIALS_IV.
	(load): new method to load the materials from a generic SoInput
	stream.
	(setDefaultMaterials): now uses an iv file, embedded into a
	string, as default, instead of creating and modifying the
	SoMaterials directly.

	* IgMatEdMainWidget.cc (createSoMaterial): now using the "name"
	field of the SoMaterial to store the material name.

	* IgMatEdMainWidget.cc (saveMaterialMap): now saves the materials
	in one single .iv file, instead of having several directories and
	files.

	* IgMatEdMainWidget.cc (IgMatEdMainWidget): modified to comply
	with the fact that IgSoMaterialMap now stores SoMaterials
	directly.

	* IgSoMaterialMap.h (IgSoMaterialMap): now the map stores
	SoMaterials directly, without need for wrapper class
	IgSoMaterialMapEntry. Added load() method which loads a .iv file
	as material map.

	* IgMatEdMainWidget.h: Does not refer anymore to class
	IgSoMaterialMap

